The '''tutakan''' was an eight-legged [[Lizard/Legends|lizard]] with huge tusks that curled up past its eyes and curled in to its head, appearing as if they were eyebrows. They were used in the city of [[Redhaven]] on [[Rhommamool/Legends|Rhommamool]] by the [[Red Knights of Life]], the fanatic followers of "[[Rhommamool/Legends|Rhommamoolian]] tyrant" [[Nom Anor]], who was secretly a [[Yuuzhan Vong]] agent and [[Executor (Yuuzhan Vong rank)|executor]] sent to sow discord in the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]]. The Red Knights would accost any individuals in the city using mechanical means of transport such as [[Landspeeder/Legends|landspeeders]] and insist that they ride tutakans instead.<ref name="Vector Prime" />

